Depends :
---------
XiVO:
- xivo-dao
- lib-python
- xivo-client-sim-1.0

HTTP/PHP:
- HTTPful

Other dependencies will be installed by the install script:
- for independent web server (temporary):
--- gevent-0.13.8, greenlet-0.4.0, tornado-2.4.1, Flask-0.9, Werkzeug-0.8.3, 
--- tornado
- for pip support (temporary)
--- binutils build-essential cpp cpp-4.4 dpkg-dev g++ g++-4.4 gcc gcc-4.4 libc-dev-bin libc6-dev libdpkg-perl libevent-1.4-2 libevent-core-1.4-2 libevent-dev libevent-extra-1.4-2 libmpfr4 libssl-dev libstdc++6-4.4-dev libtimedate-perl linux-libc-dev make python-dev python-pip python-setuptools python2.6-dev zlib1g-dev 


Installation :
--------------
use xivo-recording.tar

tar -xvf xivo-recording.tar
cd xivo-recording

Be sure to have a corresponding web interface package in the xivo-recording directory (with the support of the recording)! 
./install.sh

Patch dao (git repo xivo-dao branch recording):
xivo-dao/xivo_dao/agentfeaturesdao.py
xivo-dao/xivo_dao/queue_features_dao.py


Removing:
----------
manual

 
Packaging :
-----------
Create the tar
tar -cvf xivo-recording.tar xivo-recording/ --exclude '*.log' --exclude '.*' --exclude '*.pyc' --exclude tests --exclude acceptance

 
